# Supabase (Phase 1 team workspace) — optional, free tier at supabase.com
# Create a project, copy Project URL + anon public key, run migrations in supabase/migrations/.
# See docs/OBSERVABILITY-ZERO.md for the full $0 setup checklist.
# When unset, Meritly runs in local-only mode (localStorage audit + error log, no login).

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-publishable-key

# Auth UX (team / enterprise defaults)
VITE_ALLOW_PUBLIC_SIGNUP=false
# Optional hospital label on login panel, e.g. "Acme Health System"
# VITE_AUTH_ORG_LABEL=Acme Health System
# VITE_AUTH_REDIRECT_URL=http://localhost:5173
